expression.expression:
'SELECT DISTINCT TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,''YYYY-MM-DD'') AS CHAR_DATE, A.SUBSCRIPTION_ID, C.OS, CASE WHEN B.DL_TOTAL_30D IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE
(ROUND(B.DL_TOTAL_30D / 1024 / 1024)) END AS DL_TOTAL_30D,

FROM CM_CP.V_CAP_PROFILE as A
LEFT JOIN CM_CP.V_CAP_USAGE_DATA as B ON A.MSISDN = B.MSISDN
LEFT JOIN CM_CP.V_CAP_D_EQUIPMENT as C ON to_number(A.CURRENT_TAC) = C.TAC

WHERE 1=1 AND ((A.COS_FAMILY_PL = ''Mass'') OR (A.COS_FAMILY_PL = ''Business'' AND A.CUST_VOLUME_SEGMENT = ''SOHO'')) AND A.SERVICE_ACTIVE_FLG = 1 AND A.SUBSCRIPTION_ID IS NOT NULL

SELECT DISTINCT u.id, SELECT(
    SELECT * FROM user_data WHERE id = 1
) as data FROM user as u WHERE u.id = 1 LAST u.id'

'SELECT DISTINCT
TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,''YYYY-MM-DD'') AS CHAR_DATE,
A.SUBSCRIPTION_ID,
A.SYSDATE_WE,
A.SYSDATE,
A.ROUND,
A.SELECT,
A.COS_ID,
A.CHAR_DATE,
A.AS,
A.FROM,
A.ON_CHAR_DATE,
A.ON_NULL,
A.NULL,
A.1,
A.INSERT,
A.A,
A.DATE,
A.to_number,
A.IF,
A.ELSE,
FROM TEST AS A
LEFT JOIN TEST B ON A.ID = B.A_ID'
